Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.26,0:01:36.66,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be6\blur6\fad(312,300)}kagi wo kaketa garasu no hako ni nani wo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:42.38,OP,,0,0,0,,{\be6\blur6\fad(312,300)}kakushiteirun darou?
